Plot: An expectant couple who moves into the most haunted house in New Orleans call upon the services of the Vatican's elite exorcism team to save them from a demonic baby.
Title: Hell Baby
Actors: Rob Corddry, Leslie Bibb, Alex Berg, Keegan-Michael Key
tomatoConsensus: Though its brand of immature comedy may appeal to some, Hell Baby misses the mark with much of its humor, rendering it a largely ineffective -- and often crass -- genre sendup.
